def simple_plot(x, y, title, y_label, x_label='Date'):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))
    plt.plot(x, y, linewidth=0.8, color='red')

    #plt.xticks(
    #range(1, 13),
    #[t]
    #)

    plt.title(title)
    plt.xlabel(x_label)
    plt.ylabel(y_label)

    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

tempt_df['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(tempt_df['Date'])
tempt_df['Year'] = tempt_df['Date'].dt.year

tempt_df['Month'] = tempt_df['Date'].dt.month
years = tempt_df['Year'].unique()
In[587]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
for d, g in tempt_df.groupby('Year'):
    # average for moth by each year
    gm = g.groupby('Month', as_index=False)['mean-tempt'].mean().sort_values('Month')
    plt.plot(gm['Month'], gm['mean-tempt'], linewidth=1.2, alpha=0.9)

plt.title('Seasonal Plot for daily data')
plt.xlabel('Month')
plt.ylabel('Mean temperature')

# plt.legend()
plt.xticks(range(1, 13), ['January', 'February', 'March',
                         'April', 'May', 'June',
                         'July', 'August', 'September',
                         'October', 'November', 'December'], rotation=45)
plt.show()

aep_df = df_aep.copy()
aep_df['Datetime'] = pd.to_datetime(aep_df['Datetime'])

aep_df['Hour'] = aep_df['Datetime'].dt.strftime('%H:%M')
aep_df['Year'] = aep_df['Datetime'].dt.year

years = aep_df['Year'].unique()
hours = aep_df['Hour'].unique()
In[590]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
for d, g in aep_df.groupby('Year'):
    gm = g.groupby('Hour', as_index=False)['AEP_MW'].mean().sort_values('Hour')
    plt.plot(gm['Hour'], gm['AEP_MW'], linewidth=1.2, alpha=0.9)

plt.title('Seasonal Plot for hourly data')
plt.xlabel('Hours')
plt.ylabel('Average of AEP MW')

plt.xticks(hours, rotation=45)
